         <abstract>
            <p>An algorithm for the construction of the polynomials associated with the weight function w(t)P(t) from those associated with w(t) is given for the case when P(t) is a polynomial which is nonnegative in the interval of orthogonality. The relation of the algorithm to the LR algorithm is also discussed.</p>
          </abstract>
